WARNING: Data structures incompatible with previous version
-----------------------------------------------------------

As SP-ProjectMan 1.0x offers subprojects support, the projects and references
files organisation has been considerably changed from 0.9x.
Old organisation cannot be maintained. You have to reconstruct all of your
projects.

This may seem a big problem. In fact, as you will for sure use subprojects
feature, you'll have all the way to reconfigure your projects.

I hope I may keep the current organisation in the future releases.
Therefore, please don't make too good sugestions of improvements on that point,
Thanks! :-)






